import React from 'react'; import { format, parse, isValid, parseISO } from 'date-fns'; export function CollectionSummaryTable(props) { const paymentInfo = props.paymentInfo; const salesOfficerLocation = props.salesOfficerLocation; return ( <>
{salesOfficerLocation.location_type}
{salesOfficerLocation.location_name} 		Date of Collection
{format(parseISO(paymentInfo.paymentDate), 'dd MMM yyyy HH:mm a')}
Ditributor
{paymentInfo.distributor.distributorName} 		Payment No.
{paymentInfo.paymentNo}
Collected By
{paymentInfo.collectionBy.name}
{paymentInfo.collectionBy.designation.name}, {paymentInfo.company.name}
Reference No.
{paymentInfo.referenceNo}
); }
